          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "And placements are also good, many companies hire students and the college has better placements",
          "name": "Review Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "And the faculty members are also very educated who provide good education to the students, students are taught with practical in the lab",
