        {
          "text": "The teacher encourage students in future path",
          "name": "Review Ranger",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Axis colleges is famous for their quality of education they have provided good or relatable education to their students",
          "name": "Ayushi Saini",
          "course_tag_name": "D.Pharm"
        },
        {
          "text": "They have also provided practical knowledge by organising various visits and tours",
          "name": "Ayushi Saini",
